Woocation,gives,travelers,information,about,the,places,they,want,to,visit,The,site,does,this,by,collecting,as,much,data,as,it,can,about,a,place,The,Woocation,Cityinfo,API,provides,information,about,cities,worldwide,From,currency,to,nearest,domestic,and,international,airports,it,provides,data,which,developers,can,pick,from,to,make,new,applications,NOTE,The,nearest,airport,facility,is,only,available,for,asia,and,oceanic,continents,as,of,now,but,we,will,be,updating,this,for,whole,of,the,world,in,coming,weeks,very,very,soon